<h2>Contacts</h2>
Manuscripts should be submitted electronically, preferably in Microsoft Word, to the Editors at the following e-mail address: <a href="mailto:epxull@yahoo.com">epxull@yahoo.com</a>. If it is not possible to submit an electronic copy, send three (3) copies of the manuscript to the Editors. Non-electronic submissions require more time to administer, so authors should be aware that the processing time for their manuscripts will be longer.
<br><br>

When the authors are notified of acceptance, they will be asked to provide the final, accepted version of the article on in electronic format containing the article text files.